text:
‚ÄúLeadership beyond business - businesses must take a more societal, empathetic and sustainable approach to ensure consumer growth‚Äù
- Herjit Bhalla, Vice President, India and AEMEA, The Hershey Company @Herjit23 @HersheysIndia #PitchCMO
name: e4m(Events)

text:
‚ÄúOur products were vastly consumed, but our factories shut down in the middle amidst high demand and our employees volunteered to shift into the factory‚Äù
- Herjit Bhalla, Vice President, India and AEMEA, The Hershey Company @Herjit23 @HersheysIndia #PitchCMO
name: e4m(Events)

text:
‚ÄúOn the go leadership is relevant - being comfortable with chaos, confusion and uncertainty‚Äù 
- Herjit Bhalla, Vice President, India and AEMEA, The Hershey Company @Herjit23 @HersheysIndia #PitchCMO
name: e4m(Events)

text:
‚ÄúWe started ‚Äòstronger and growing together‚Äô 3 years back, the purpose being ‚Äòlook after your employees, they‚Äôll look after your business‚Äù 
- Herjit Bhalla, Vice President, India and AEMEA, The Hershey Company @Herjit23 @HersheysIndia #PitchCMO
name: e4m(Events)

text:
‚ÄúEmployee well-being is key. If your people are happy, the work flows. The hybrid work model is adaptable‚Äù
-Herjit Bhalla, Vice President, India and AEMEA, The Hershey Company @Herjit23 @HersheysIndia #PitchCMO
name: e4m(Events)

text:
‚ÄúBuilding brands with purpose and relevance is key. Lifebuoy has done a great job through the pandemic with respect to this‚Äù 
- Herjit Bhalla, Vice President, India and AEMEA, The Hershey Company @Herjit23 @HersheysIndia #PitchCMO
name: e4m(Events)

text:
‚ÄúOur founder said ‚Äògive them quality. That‚Äôs the best kind of advertising in the world‚Äô. Priority is providing fantastic consumer experience‚Äù 
- Herjit Bhalla, Vice President, India and AEMEA, The Hershey Company @Herjit23 @HersheysIndia #PitchCMO
name: e4m(Events)

text:
‚ÄúSignificant changes took place at a more humane level, people are the key to future proofing businesses- build deeper connections‚Äù 
- Herjit Bhalla, Vice President, India and AEMEA, The Hershey Company @Herjit23 @HersheysIndia #PitchCMO
name: e4m(Events)

text:
‚ÄúConsumer behaviour has changed, the kitchen is now a ‚Äòhappy place‚Äô, BFY became the buzzword and e-comm grew massively‚Äù 
- Herjit Bhalla, Vice President, India and AEMEA, The Hershey Company @Herjit23 @HersheysIndia #PitchCMO
name: e4m(Events)
